# ADC running average over rolling window.
*roll_avg(s as Vec of i64, n as i64, w as i64) returns i64
    sum is 0
    i is n - w
    while i < n
        sum is sum + s.get(i)
        i is i + 1
    sum / w

*main
    s is vec()
    i is 0
    while i < 20
        s.push(500 + (i * 13) % 50)
        i is i + 1
    log roll_avg(s, 20, 5)
